  "title": "QUANTITY SURVEYOR – LTA PROJECT (CIVIL WORK)",
  "description": "<p><strong>• Remuneration package: $4,000 to $6,500</strong></p><p><strong>• Top Leading Construction Company</strong></p><p><strong>• LTA Project</strong><br /></p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>To study & understand tender drawings & contract document.</p></li><li><p>BQ for tender or variation submission.</p></li><li><p>Preparing substantiation document for claim purpose.</p></li><li><p>Ensure tender or VO submission is on time.</p></li><li><p>Sourcing quotation from subcon and supplier and carry out comparison of quotation.</p></li><li><p>Taking off quantities for tenders or site projects.</p></li><li><p>Pre-tender/ site project estimates and prepare documentation.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirement</strong></p><ul><li><p>Diploma or Degree in Quantity Surveying or related</p></li><li><p>At least 2 years of QS experience</p></li><li><p>Experience with LTA project<br /></p></li></ul><p>All Successful candidates can expect a very competitive remuneration package and a comprehensive range of benefits.</p><p>Kindly email your resume in a detailed Word format to<br /></p><p><a href=\"mailto:roy.yeo@peopleprofilers.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">roy.yeo@peopleprofilers.com</a><br /></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified</p><p>People Profilers Pte Ltd</p><p>20 Cecil Street, #08-09 PLUS Building Singapore 049705</p><p>EA License Number: 02C4944</p><p>Registration Number: R1217882</p><p>Posting Personnel: Yeo Yi Rong</p><p><a href=\"tel:6950 9757\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">6950 9757</a></p>",
